Class TypedQuery<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.querydsl.lucene4.AbstractLuceneQuery<T,TypedQuery<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - result type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Fetchable<T>, FilteredClause<TypedQuery<T>>, SimpleQuery<TypedQuery<T>>

    public class TypedQuery<T>
extends AbstractLuceneQuery<T,TypedQuery<T>>
    TypedQuery is a typed query implementation for Lucene queries.

    Converts Lucene documents to typed results via a constructor supplied transformer

    Author:
    laim, tiwe
